Aisha Buhari, Wife of President Muhammadu Buhari has deactivate her Twitter page. Aisha made the announcement before deactivating it on Friday night. DAILY POST had reported that the Minister of Information, Lai Mohammed, on Friday announced the suspension of the social blogging site. The suspension is not unconnected to President Buhari’s controversial tweet that was deleted by the management of Twitter on Wednesday. She tweeted, “I will be deactivating my Twitter account for now. “Long live Federal Republic of Nigeria.”